        <title>解决Firefox网页上小图标在强制使用字体后不显示的问题</title>
        <link>https://hyruo.com/article/2014-01-08-wordpress/</link>
        <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2014 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://hyruo.com/article/2014-01-08-wordpress/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="https://hyruo.com/article/2014-01-08-wordpress/firefox.png" alt="Featured image of post 解决Firefox网页上小图标在强制使用字体后不显示的问题" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;用Firefox时，经常会遇到网站后台图标不显示的问题，甚至发现有Wordpress后台编辑器等图标按钮全部丢失不显示的情况。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2014-01-08-wordpress/images/6248.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;481&#34;
	height=&#34;101&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2014-01-08-wordpress/images/6248_hu7411f07342fef9b15ce642e0eba76b77_10294_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/2014-01-08-wordpress/images/6248_hu7411f07342fef9b15ce642e0eba76b77_10294_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;476&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;1142px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在Google一顿乱搜未明结果，仔细观察这些图标上显示的文字，发现都是F101 F102 F103 F201 F202 F303这种，于是想到可能是字体问题。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Firefox等浏览器的字体设置中有是否限制网站选择字体使用的选项，之前为了字体渲染方便直接禁用了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2014-01-08-wordpress/images/62481.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;474&#34;
	height=&#34;416&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2014-01-08-wordpress/images/62481_hu36656025ea48084396dca7f48b4aa9c4_51167_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/2014-01-08-wordpress/images/62481_hu36656025ea48084396dca7f48b4aa9c4_51167_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;113&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;273px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;修改后问题得以解决。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2014-01-08-wordpress/images/62482.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;482&#34;
	height=&#34;106&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2014-01-08-wordpress/images/62482_hucf910804b56838582b59864ce3f561ca_10595_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/2014-01-08-wordpress/images/62482_hucf910804b56838582b59864ce3f561ca_10595_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;454&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;1091px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;但是，如果“允许页面选择字体”，遇上国内一大堆使用各种蛋疼字体的网站，那无疑是非常郁闷的了。所以，一劳永逸的办法是将图标所使用的字体添加到Stylish里边。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2014-01-08-wordpress/images/6286.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;743&#34;
	height=&#34;521&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2014-01-08-wordpress/images/6286_hub2dc9666e6e28d9e15c0ff3cdb5ea782_96631_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/2014-01-08-wordpress/images/6286_hub2dc9666e6e28d9e15c0ff3cdb5ea782_96631_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;142&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;342px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;使用Firefox的元素查看器可以非常容易看到，Wordpress后台MCE编辑器所使用的图标字体为font-family:&amp;ldquo;Dashicons&amp;rdquo;;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;于是将Dashicons添加到Stylish即可。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2014-01-08-wordpress/images/6287.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1020&#34;
	height=&#34;539&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2014-01-08-wordpress/images/6287_hu11310f74853d9cfb278b4aa684b97cc1_106248_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/2014-01-08-wordpress/images/6287_hu11310f74853d9cfb278b4aa684b97cc1_106248_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;189&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;454px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;4
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;5
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;6
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt;7
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-fallback&#34; data-lang=&#34;fallback&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;@namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;@-moz-document regexp(&amp;#34;((?!XYZ.com).)*&amp;#34;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;{
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;*{font-family:rei,iconfont,FontAwesome,Octicons,Icomoon,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Open Sans,dashicons,微软雅黑 !important;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;这里已经添加了网络上常用的图标字体了。
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2014-01-08-wordpress/images/6288.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;663&#34;
	height=&#34;478&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://hyruo.com/article/2014-01-08-wordpress/images/6288_hu1f9168b442f0ceeffdee468f3d7469d5_85652_480x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 480w, https://hyruo.com/article/2014-01-08-wordpress/images/6288_hu1f9168b442f0ceeffdee468f3d7469d5_85652_1024x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;138&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;332px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
